data.description: Welcome Home! Entering on the first floor you will find a large and open floorplan with plenty of functionality. On your left you will find a powder room, laundry area and a bonus room perfect for a home office / den / play room. The dining room on your right flows openly in to the spacious kitchen with stainless steel appliances, ceramic backsplash and plenty of counter and cabinet space. Off the kitchen step outside to your patio area and access to your storage shed with electricity! Entering the generous size family room you will enjoy plenty of natural light and a gas fireplace. Upstairs welcomes you to 3 sizable bedrooms and a hallway full bathroom. The master suite offers a walk in closet and spacious ensuite. The lower level provides space to entertain and also be used as an additional living room / office space. Playground across the street and Route 51 shops / restaurants nearby! Make 515 Galileo your next home!
